# CODEOWNERS for Portfolio & Delivery AI Technology Radar
#
# This file defines who can approve changes to different parts of the radar.
# Teams own their own directories and can approve changes to their blips.
#
# Documentation: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/user/project/codeowners/

# Default owners for the entire repository
* @pnd/ai/radar-maintainers

# Core repository files - require approval from maintainers
/README.md @pnd/ai/radar-maintainers
/.gitlab-ci.yml @pnd/ai/radar-maintainers
/scripts/ @pnd/ai/radar-maintainers
/CODEOWNERS @pnd/ai/radar-maintainers

# Radar entries
# Teams can own specific entries by file path

# Example entries
/radar/platforms/kubernetes.md @your-user-name @another-username
/radar/tools/gitlab-ci.md @whatever
/radar/tips/python.md @also-here

# Add your team's ownership here:
# /radar/<quadrant>/<entry-name>.md @your-team-lead @team-member1 @team-member2
